            </li>

            <li class="[counter-increment:item] before:content-[counter(item)'.'] before:font-bold before:text-investipal-600 before:mr-3">
              This Site is only intended to provide you with general information and is neither an offer to sell nor a solicitation of an offer to purchase any security and may not be relied upon for investment purposes.
            </li>

            <li class="[counter-increment:item] before:content-[counter(item)'.'] before:font-bold before:text-investipal-600 before:mr-3">
              Any commentaries and information contained in the Site should not be considered personal investment advice.
            </li>

            <li class="[counter-increment:item] before:content-[counter(item)'.'] before:font-bold before:text-investipal-600 before:mr-3">
